You can get the Flex 4 SDK at:
http://opensource.adobe.com/wiki/display/flexsdk/Download+Flex+4

Flex 4 SDK is assumed to be installed in $FLEX_ROOT
Make sure that
<omit-trace-statements>false</omit-trace-statements>
is set to false in
$FLEX_ROOT/frameworks/flex-config.xml

To compile tests inside the tests/ directory use the following command:
$FLEX_ROOT/bin/mxmlc -static-link-runtime-shared-libraries test.mxml -output test.swf
